{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7393de38c0","title":"关于购买空军装备器材致斯大林电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e024f191bc","index":0,"year":1950,"month":4,"day":13,"articleId":"7393de38c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f61969d2fb","type":"title","text":"关于购买空军装备器材致斯大林电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"9f8199920a","type":"paragraph","text":"莫斯科斯大林同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"467c1ef5c6","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国人民革命军事委员会，预定一九五〇年六月间进行夺取舟山群岛的作战，八月间进行夺取金门岛的作战。上述两次作战将有已经训练出来的中国空军部队（两个驱逐机团，一个轰炸机团）参加。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"ad7067fc75","type":"paragraph","text":"由于其余的十四个空军团（根据种种条件所限，拟改变原来计划为七个驱逐机团，七个轰炸机团）要明年春天才能训练出来，夺取台湾的作战，准备一九五一年进行之。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"f19edaa997","type":"paragraph","text":"为了保证中国空军部队在上述作战中的行动，请求你允许我们高苏联购买空军用的各种机械器材、特种车辆、备份零件、油料和弹药，并请按各个订货单内所规定的期限发货。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"b1348569c8","type":"paragraph","text":"上述物资的订货单十四件，随函附上","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"044b233807","type":"paragraph","text":"谨致共产主义的敬礼！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"a4a85fc2ee","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"},{"id":"39d0dcc96b","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年四月十三日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0"}],"page":{"id":"6e4fe56513","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"7393de38c0","start":274,"end":274}}}},"__N_SSG":true}